{"ts":"2026-07-18T10:08:48.018Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-tmhs"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-592: tracker_not_initialized recovery re-suggests pm init even when a --pm-path tracker exists — following it silently splits workspace state"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"GitHub issue #592 (GH-501 residue): a workspace initialized with --pm-path <custom> still fails bare commands with tracker_not_initialized, and the recovery bundle re-suggests pm init — creating a second tracker at <cwd>/.agents/pm and silently splitting workspace state. Fix = recovery bundle documents that discovery probes .agents/pm only and names --pm-path/PM_PATH; ideally detects an existing non-default tracker nearby (e.g. <cwd>/.pm or one level down) and suggests the exact --pm-path invocation instead of init. Capability-aware hint-rendering family (pm-qljv class)."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","init","recovery-hints"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-18T10:08:48.018Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-18T10:08:48.018Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":150},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"tracker_not_initialized recovery names --pm-path/PM_PATH and the .agents/pm-only discovery rule; nearby non-default tracker detection suggests the concrete --pm-path command instead of pm init; no false-positive suggestions from unrelated settings.json files; regression coverage including the GH-501 positional-init fixed path"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-mpbb"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"medium"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"pm-kvev","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-18T10:08:48.018Z"},{"id":"pm-qljv","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-18T10:08:48.018Z"},{"id":"pm-surv","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-18T10:08:48.018Z"}]}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"09cf0a764ac07c55151020855ba5867ebe11c2f92a870c783f5d9c375a597074","message":""}
